[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0246","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0246.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0687","title":"Sun Solaris ToolTalk ttsession 守护进程远程代码执行漏洞","description":"ToolTalk ttsession 守护进程使用弱 RPC 认证机制（AUTH_UNIX），未启用更强的 AUTH_DES 认证，导致未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该漏洞绕过认证直接执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 2.3~7.0 以及 HP-UX 等多种 Unix 操作系统版本，攻击者无需本地访问权限即可远程利用，导致系统完全受控。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0687"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-13","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.907","remediation":"安装 Sun Security Bulletin #192 中提供的对应 Solaris 版本（2.3~7.0）补丁程序，或升级到已修复此问题的 Solaris 8 及以上版本。如无法升级，可在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 ttsession 服务行并重启 inetd 以禁用 ToolTalk 服务，同时在网络层面限制对 RPC 端口（111/TCP/UDP）的访问。对于 HP-UX 系统，请参考 HP Security Bulletin HPSBUX9909-103 安装对应补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/192","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/k-001.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/637","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9909-103"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0246.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0450","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0450.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0751","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server Accept 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 3.6 版本（安装了 SSL Handshake Patch）的 Accept 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向服务器发送特制的 Accept 请求头，触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃或可能执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Netscape Enterprise Server 3.51 及 3.6 SP2 版本，CVSS v2.0 评分 5.0，危害等级中危，攻击向量为网络远程攻击，无需认证即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0751"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1999-09-13","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Netscape Enterprise Server 已于 2007 年停止支持，官方不再提供安全更新。建议立即迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server、Nginx 或 IIS），并彻底停用旧版 Netscape 服务器。如无法立即迁移，应在防火墙层面限制对 80/443 端口的访问来源，仅允许可信 IP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/631","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3256"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0450.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0450.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0450.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0711","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0711.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0910","title":"Microsoft Site Server 和 MCIS Cookie 未设置过期时间漏洞","description":"Microsoft Site Server 及商业 Internet 系统（MCIS）在生成会话 Cookie 时未设置过期时间，导致 Cookie 默认仅在浏览器会话期间有效，但可在会话结束后被重放利用。远程攻击者通过窃取或截获未设置过期时间的 Cookie，可冒充合法用户身份访问受保护的 Web 资源，导致会话劫持和信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Site Server 及 MCIS 系列产品。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0910"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-10","updated":"1999-09-10","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-035 提供的修补程序，该补丁修复了 Site Server/MCIS 在 Set-Cookie 响应中缺少过期头的问题。如无法立即更新，可配置代理服务器不缓存包含 Set-Cookie 头的页面，并关闭基于纯 Cookie 的身份验证机制作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0711.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0273","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0273.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0697","title":"SCO Doctor 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SCO Doctor 管理工具中存在权限提升漏洞，本地用户可通过该工具的 \"Tools\" 选项以 root 权限执行任意操作。攻击者需拥有系统本地访问权限，利用该漏洞可完全控制受影响系统，包括修改系统配置、访问敏感数据及安装恶意程序。该漏洞影响 SCO OpenServer 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议用户限制本地用户对 SCO Doctor 工具的访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0697"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.187","remediation":"升级 SCO OpenServer 至 5.0.5 及以上版本，或安装 SCO 官方安全补丁 erg712103。如无法升级，移除 SCO Doctor 的 setuid root 权限（chmod u-s /opt/K/SCO/Doctor/1.0.0/bin/doctor），并限制可登录系统的本地用户账号数量，仅保留管理员可交互登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/621","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0697.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0697","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0697.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0697.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fwr5-hvj8-gff6/GHSA-fwr5-hvj8-gff6.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0697.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6229833c-4cf2-4d79-b4d0-ced5f5ebb24d.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0273.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1091","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1091.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1377","title":"Matt Wright download.cgi 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"download.cgi 1.0 存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 f 参数传入 `../` 等目录跳转序列，绕过访问限制读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞源于程序未对用户输入的文件路径进行充分过滤和规范化处理，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，可能导致敏感配置文件、系统文件等泄露。影响运行 Matt Wright's download.cgi 1.0 的 Web 服务器。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1377"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:18.610","remediation":"立即停止使用 Matt Wright 的 download.cgi 1.0 脚本，该脚本已停止维护且无安全更新。彻底删除服务器上所有 download.cgi 文件，或通过 Web 服务器配置（如 Apache 的 <Location> 指令）限制对该脚本的访问。如必须使用，在 CGI 脚本中对 f 参数进行路径规范化过滤，拒绝包含 ../ 或 %2e%2e/ 等目录遍历序列的输入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://pulhas.org/phrack/55/P55-07.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1091.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0482","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0482.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0767","title":"Sun Solaris 及 IBM AIX LC_MESSAGES 环境变量 libc 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统的 libc 库、ufsrestore 及 rcp 工具中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过设置特制的 LC_MESSAGES 环境变量触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，进而实现权限提升或以目标进程权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 7.0 及 IBM AIX 4.2.1 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0767"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.953","remediation":"建议安装 Sun 安全补丁 106815-01 (Solaris 7) 或升级至 Solaris 8 及以上版本；AIX 用户应安装 APAR IX89654 或升级至 AIX 4.3.3。临时缓解措施：在系统层面限制 LC_MESSAGES 环境变量长度，或通过 setuid 程序过滤环境变量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420557&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19217"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0482.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1070","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1070.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1353","title":"Nosque MsgCore 明文密码存储漏洞","description":"Nosque MsgCore 2.14 存在密码明文存储漏洞，管理员密码以明文形式保存在注册表 AdmPasswd 键中，用户密码以明文形式存储在 Userbase.dbf 数据文件中。本地攻击者可通过读取注册表或数据库文件直接获取凭证，进而提升权限并完全控制系统，影响机密性与完整性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1353"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-07","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议升级至 MsgCore 2.15 或更高版本；如厂商已停止维护，应使用 Windows 注册表 ACL 限制 AdmPasswd 键仅允许管理员读取，对 Userbase.dbf 设置 NTFS 权限仅允许管理员访问并启用 EFS 加密，同时确保服务器物理安全。建议迁移至其他支持安全密码存储的邮件服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93698162708211&w=2","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1353"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1070.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0725","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0725.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0925","title":"Messagemedia UnityMail 2.0 MIME Header 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"MessageMedia UnityMail 2.0 邮件服务器在处理邮件 MIME 头部时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标服务器发送包含大量 MIME 头的特制邮件，导致服务程序因资源耗尽而崩溃，影响正常邮件收发功能。该漏洞影响 UnityMail 2.0 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。厂商已发布相关安全公告。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0925"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:20.490","remediation":"建议升级至 UnityMail 2.1 或更高版本，该版本已在 MIME 解析器中加入头部数量限制。若供应商已停止支持该产品，应迁移至仍在维护的邮件服务器软件（如 Postfix、Exchange），并在边界邮件网关配置 MIME 头部数量阈值（建议≤100 个）作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90486243124867&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0725.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1309","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1309.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0926","title":"Apache HTTP Server MIME Header 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Apache HTTP Server 1.2.5 及 1.3.1 版本在处理大量 MIME 头部时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证，通过向目标服务器发送包含大量 MIME 头部的特制 HTTP 请求，可耗尽服务器资源致其崩溃，无法响应正常请求。该漏洞利用简单，攻击门槛低，受影响版本包括 Apache 1.2.5/1.3.1 及 UnityMail 2.0。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0926"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:20.597","remediation":"升级至 Apache HTTP Server 1.3.2 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法立即升级，可在 httpd.conf 中通过 `LimitRequestFields` 指令限制请求头字段数量，减小 MIME 头泛滥导致拒绝服务的攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/1998_3/0742.html","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20272"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1309.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0244","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0244.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0685","title":"Netscape Communicator EMBED 标签缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.06至4.61版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向用户发送嵌有恶意EMBED标签的HTML页面，在pluginspage选项中构造超长字符串触发缓冲区溢出，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响Netscape Communicator 4.x系列多个版本，攻击者需诱使用户访问特制网页，无需额外认证即可完成利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0685"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-09-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.657","remediation":"升级 Netscape Communicator 至 4.7 及以上版本，该版本修复了通过 EMBED 标签 pluginspage 选项触发的缓冲区溢出漏洞。鉴于 Netscape 已停止维护，建议迁移至 Mozilla Firefox 或 Google Chrome 等现代浏览器。如无法升级，可在浏览器设置中禁用 Java/插件支持作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/618","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19486","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0685.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0685","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0685.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc69cd1e5221f68ef56bd10c5c61adf76a19f0fc/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0685.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/44d84714e9a3b4364d62f8189e2d74dba61b570e/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qr94-86r9-f9hg/GHSA-qr94-86r9-f9hg.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0685.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0244.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0244.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0244.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1073","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1073.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1356","title":"Compaq Insight Manager agent Integration Maintenance Utility 法律通告篡改漏洞","description":"Compaq Insight Manager agent 中的 Integration Maintenance Utility 组件在 SmartStart 4.50 之前版本中存在配置篡改漏洞。该工具可修改 Windows NT 系统的登录法律通知标题（LegalNoticeCaption）和文本（LegalNoticeText），导致安全策略中规定的法律声明被篡改或绕过。攻击者利用该工具可覆盖系统登录时的法律提示内容，使其不符合企业安全合规要求，从而削弱系统安全管理机制。此漏洞需要本地访问权限，危害程度中等，影响使用 Compaq Insight Manager agent 的 Windows NT 系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1356"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:15.973","remediation":"升级 Compaq Insight Manager agent 至 SmartStart 4.50 或更高版本，该版本修复了 Integration Maintenance Utility 可被伪造请求修改 Windows NT 法律声明的问题。如无法升级，建议限制对 Compaq Insight Manager agent 管理端口的网络访问权限，仅允许受信任主机连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93646669500991&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93637792706047&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93759822830815&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7763.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1356.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1356","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1356.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1356.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p5mv-6mvr-j99h/GHSA-p5mv-6mvr-j99h.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87889/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1356.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000761.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5cf7a56c-2fdc-4fd8-b7ba-076f2fd947b8.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1073.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1148","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1148.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1516","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16328,\"outputTokens\":46,\"totalTokens\":16374}}","description":"TenFour TFS Gateway SMTP 邮件服务器 3.2 版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者通过向 SMTP 服务的 MAIL FROM 命令中发送超过 128 字节的特制字符串即可触发该溢出，导致邮件服务器崩溃，并可能进而执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行 TenFour TFS Gateway SMTP 3.2 的服务器，未经身份认证的远程攻击者即可利用，无需特殊权限或交互条件。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1516"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:36.473","remediation":"TenFour 官方已在 TFS SMTP Gateway 4.0 中修复该缓冲区溢出漏洞。建议立即将 TenFour TFS Gateway SMTP 服务器从 3.2 升级至 4.0 或更高版本。如暂时无法升级，可通过在防火墙或邮件网关处对 SMTP 连接中 MAIL FROM 命令的数据长度进行限制（拒绝超过 128 字节的字符串）作为临时缓解措施，并监控邮件服务器日志以发现异常连接断开。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93677241318492&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c271719fd48dcc28619dc324e441b822d7b4bace/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1516.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1516","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1516.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1516.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/907ae4099f60f85a9473cd7e47129d370c445f83/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x657-67f8-62qq/GHSA-x657-67f8-62qq.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1516.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/T/tfs_smtp_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000762.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8200d63179d89b9076027cd96356d55ef8a5349e/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1148.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0196","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0196.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0669","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4/5 ActiveX Eyedog 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0 和 5.0 版本中的 Eyedog ActiveX 控件被错误标记为\"可安全执行脚本\"，导致远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页诱导用户访问，利用该控件执行任意命令。该漏洞已由 Bubbleboy 蠕虫证实存在实际利用，影响早期 Windows 系统上的 IE 浏览器用户，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0669"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.617","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 6 或更高版本，或使用现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome）替代。在 IE 中设置 ActiveX 控件为「禁用」或「提示」，并通过注册表设置 Kill Bit（CLSID: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000）禁用 Eyedog ActiveX 控件。对于无法升级的系统，在 Internet 安全区域将「下载已签名的 ActiveX 控件」设为「禁用」以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-064.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19487"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0196.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0196.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0196.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0202","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0202.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0670","title":"Eyedog ActiveX 控件缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Eyedog ActiveX 控件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造特制网页诱使用户访问，触发缓冲区溢出从而执行任意命令。该漏洞影响了 Internet Explorer 浏览器中集成的 Eyedog ActiveX 控件，攻击者需要诱导用户打开恶意网页或包含恶意内容的电子邮件才能成功利用，危害较大。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0670"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.737","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 于 1999 年 8 月发布的安全公告 MS99-032 对应补丁（KB240308），或通过 Windows Update 更新至最新版本的 Internet Explorer。该补丁为 Eyedog ActiveX 控件设置 kill bit，阻止其在 IE 中加载。作为手动缓解措施，可在注册表 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\ActiveX Compatibility 下为 CLSID {A5ECB622-137C-11D2-B34D-00C04FB6F6E1} 创建 Compatibility Flags 值为 0x400 的 DWORD 项，同样可禁用该控件。长远建议升级至现代操作系统及浏览器，因较新版本已不再包含此控件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-064.shtml","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-032","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0670.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0670","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0670.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0670.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/25a429f7c036c8b0416069b51c2af695a6b890c2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vw7j-x4wv-gff4/GHSA-vw7j-x4wv-gff4.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0670.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88352/info.html","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0202.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0400","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0400.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0705","title":"ISC INN inews 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ISC INN（InterNetNews）新闻服务器中的 inews 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的新闻文章数据触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，进而可能造成拒绝服务或在目标系统上以 news 用户权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 ISC INN 2.2 及 RedHat Linux 6.0 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0705"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.177","remediation":"升级 ISC INN 至 2.3 或更高版本，该版本已修复 inews 缓冲区溢出漏洞。Red Hat Linux 6.0 用户应安装厂商提供的对应安全更新包。如无法升级，建议限制 inews 程序的 SUID 权限并仅允许受信用户访问新闻服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/616","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19480","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/10323cb4135457b41074412d623aa2116c4e1200/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0705.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0705","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0705.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4efc2590fd3e232024591793a186ed6577aaac2a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0705.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdec8f567bb266b7b6813bda45223a258023f538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-43p9-vj97-wmgv/GHSA-43p9-vj97-wmgv.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/inn.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0705.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/616/info.html","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990907.data","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0400.toml"}]